=== Ingredients ===
1 cup flour
1 cup oats
½ cup sugar
½ cup brown sugar
½ tsp salt
½ tsp soda

½ cup shortening
1 egg
½ tsp vanilla

6 oz chocolate chips
6 oz coconut (or ½ cup walnuts)

=== Directions ===
Briefly mix together dry ingredients (flour,oats,sugar,brown sugar,salt,soda)
in a mixer.  Add wet ingredients (shortening,egg,vanilla) and begin mixing.  Add
a little water if the dough is too dry.  Finally, add the chocolate chips and,
optionally, coconut or walnuts.

Spoon out rough blobs on a baking sheet and bake 10-12 minutes at 325F.
